Consider the following OpenQASM 3 fragment:
```python
bit[1] c;
qubit[1] q;
reset q[0];
rx(1.5708) q[0];
measure q[0] -> c[0];
if (c[0] == 1) {
    z q[0];
}
```
What behavior should a corresponding Qiskit circuit reproduce?

